data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Check out this Charming Home set on 15 beautiful Acres. This 4 bedroom 2 bath home is located with easy access to West Rome, Summerville, and Armuchee. The home features a large Master bedroom and bath with two walk-in closets. The remaining bedrooms all have walk-in closets for extra storage. The front porch has views of Taylors Ridge. The screened-in back porch offers peaceful views of the forest. Deer and turkey frequently wander the backyard. There is a portion of the backyard that is fenced in for your dogs to run and play. There is a 3-car garage attached to the home with room to store all of your extra items. A storage shed and metal carport come with the home for storage of outdoor equipment. This home is perfect for a growing family or a family wanting a quiet home life. Schedule an appointment today to see this beautiful home today, you will not be disappointed.
